ennet_themes.Rd

Themes from en-net forum retrieved on 17 January 2021

ennet_themes

Format

A tibble with 18 rows and 2 columns:

VariableDescription
themesThematic areas in the en-net forum
linksURL of the thematic area

Source

https://www.en-net.org
